#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Terminology]
#title[Trivial tangent bundle]

Let $M$ be a #link("009D")[manifold] of dimension $n$. We call the tangent bundle $T M$ trivial if we find $n$ pointwise linearly independent #link("009S")[vectorfields]. I.e vectorfields $X_1, ... , X_(n) in Gamma(T M)$ such that for all $x in M$ $(X_1(x), ..., X_n(x))$ is linearly independent.
